<P>What kind of monument did the immertal
<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">ervey make choice of for him&s;elf? "Let
<PB N="54" REF="54">
me," &s;ays he, "leave a memorial in the brea&s;ts
