<P>But were a body of men a<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">tificers (be their
conduct or morals as they may) to offer a re|pre&s;entation
of grievances, doubtle&s;s their ca&s;e
would be hea<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">d, and con&s;idered, in every &s;en&s;e
