recital of the&s;e heavy expences or grievances,
far<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">her than is ab&s;olutely nece&s;&s;ary; for a &s;hort
reflection mu&s;t convince every enquirer, that
to countenance this evil precedent, is not only
